OL,3,CSnoop Dogg welcomed to Swansea City
OL,4,Cfor first match as club co-owner
OL,6,FSwansea City co-owner Snoop Dogg
OL,7,Freceived a warm welcome at his first
OL,8,Fhome game since investing in the
OL,9,FChampionship club.
OL,11,FThe American rapper, who is a minority
OL,12,Fowner of the Sky Bet Championship club
OL,13,Falongside American television host
OL,14,FMartha Stewart and Croatia
OL,15,Finternational Luka Modric, made his
OL,16,Ffirst appearance at the Swansea.com
OL,17,FStadium on Tuesday, 24 February, for
OL,18,Fthe team's clash with Preston North
OL,19,FEnd.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
