OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1772025561
OL,3,CSnoop Dogg welcomed to Swansea City
OL,4,Cfor first match as club co-owner
OL,6,FThe musician, 54, visited a club
OL,7,Ftraining session and performed at a
OL,8,Fgig in Llansamlet the night before the
OL,9,Fmatch, and was seen signing fans'
OL,10,Fautographs and posing for photos on
OL,11,Fhis way into the stadium ahead of kick-
OL,12,Foff.
OL,14,FHe had requested a sold-out crowd to
OL,15,Fbe in their seats ahead of kick-off to
OL,16,Ftwirl complimentary towels ` a staple
OL,17,Faction for supporters in American
OL,18,Fsport.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
