PN,46303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1772025561
OL,3,CSnoop Dogg welcomed to Swansea City
OL,4,Cfor first match as club co-owner
OL,6,FDressed in the club's all-white
OL,7,Fcolours, with a Swansea crest on his
OL,8,Fjacket, dark glasses and a beanie hat,
OL,9,FSnoop made a pre-match lap of honour
OL,10,Fas fans twirled their towels with rock
OL,11,Fmusic booming in the background.
OL,13,FSnoop Dogg saluted the fans, shook
OL,14,Fhands with some, and had photographs
OL,15,Ftaken with others. Club mascot Cyril
OL,16,Fthe Swan even got a hug.
OL,18,FHe eventually disappeared down the
OL,19,Ftunnel seven minutes later just before
OL,20,Fa light show started prior to kick-off.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
