OL,3,CSnoop Dogg welcomed to Swansea City
OL,4,Cfor first match as club co-owner
OL,6,FHe previously said: "I know it has
OL,7,Fbeen a long time coming, but I cannot
OL,8,Fwait to finally make my first visit to
OL,9,FSwansea.
OL,11,F"From the moment we talked about me
OL,12,Fbecoming an owner, I have been looking
OL,13,Fforward to the chance to be with you
OL,14,Fall at the Swansea.com Stadium.
OL,16,F"I have heard so many great things
OL,17,Fabout the atmosphere, especially when
OL,18,Fwe play under the lights.
OL,26,@nD@UOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
