CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1772025561
OL,3,CSnoop Dogg welcomed to Swansea City
OL,4,Cfor first match as club co-owner
OL,6,F"When I watched the Wrexham game,
OL,7,Fwhere we showed we are the capital of
OL,8,FWelsh football, the noise in the
OL,9,Fstadium sounded incredible even from
OL,10,Fover 5,000 miles away. I can't wait to
OL,11,Fbe a part of it."
