OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1772025561
OL,3,CSnoop Dogg welcomed to Swansea City
OL,4,Cfor first match as club co-owner
OL,6,FThe rapper hit headlines at the Winter
OL,7,FOlympics, where he was an honorary
OL,8,Fcoach for Team USA as well as a
OL,9,Fspecial correspondent for broadcaster
OL,10,FNBC, when he asked British curlers
OL,11,FBruce Mouat and Jennifer Dodds for a
OL,12,Fphoto.Snoop Dogg, known for hits like
OL,13,FGin and Juice, has had a successful
OL,14,Fthree-decade music career, having
OL,15,Ftopped the UK charts and received 16
OL,16,FGrammy nominations.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/6
